# --- Asset 1: Karlsruhe Parking Garage HD Map ---

<did:web:provider35.net:HdMap:karlsruhe-parking-garage-001> a hdmap:HdMap ;
  rdfs:label "Karlsruhe Parking Garage HD Map"@en ;
